data.description: Texas heat is no problem for this home two brand new HVAC systems! Both units were fully replaced  this summer, new windows in living room, new flooring and to round it out the whole house has been updated with a fresh coat of neutral paint. This family home is ready to welcome it's new family this Hoilday Season. All 4 bedroom are located on the second level with laundry room.  Home offers fours bedroom two and half baths. As you enter you are welcomed with a two story entry that leads you into formal dinning and living room. Living room offers wood floors, woodburning fireplace and 4 large windows newly replaced and entergy efficient to watch over the backyard.  Enjoy your evening on the huge back patio.  This home is located in desired neighborhood of Walden on Lake Conroe and offers many community amenities.
